.6-8-8-8H360c-4.4 0-8 3.6-8 8v16c0 4.4 3.6 8 8 8z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPeter Schmalfeldt\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\tWelcome to the Unofficial Salesforce Commerce Cloud Podcast. We created this Podcast to give everyone access to each other to share ideas and help one another. It also offers members a place to discuss, listen and watch Salesforce B2C Commerce Cloud in a free and open environment.\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t<p>We can only start the list of podcasts by putting the Unofficial SFCC podcast at the top! It is the only one primarily focused on Salesforce B2C Commerce Cloud. </p><p>Various topics are discussed, going from development to recruitment within the ecosystem.</p><p><i><b>Note: </b>It has been a while since a new episode was released. Hopefully, new episodes are in the making!</i></p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>Salesforce Commerce Cloud Innovations</h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/ca/podcast/salesforce-commerce-cloud-innovations/id1654981816\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M326.612 185.391c59.747 59.809 58.927 155.698.36 214.59-.11.12-.24.25-.36.37l-67.2 67.2c-59.27 59.27-155.699 59.262-214.96 0-59.27-59.26-59.27-155.7 0-214.96l37.106-37.106c9.84-9.84 26.786-3.3 27.294 10.606.648 17.722 3.826 35.527 9.69 52.721 1.986 5.822.567 12.262-3.783 16.612l-13.087 13.087c-28.026 28.026-28.905 73.66-1.155 101.96 28.024 28.579 74.086 28.749 102.325.51l67.2-67.19c28.191-28.191 28.073-73.757 0-101.83-3.701-3.694-7.429-6.564-10.341-8.569a16.037 16.037 0 0 1-6.947-12.606c-.396-10.567 3.348-21.456 11.698-29.806l21.054-21.055c5.521-5.521 14.182-6.199 20.584-1.731a152.482 152.482 0 0 1 20.522 17.197zM467.547 44.449c-59.261-59.262-155.69-59.27-214.96 0l-67.2 67.2c-.1